  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An attack on Panadura railway station today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Angry people attacked the Panadura railway station this afternoon (13) and damaged many properties due to the sudden suspension of the train.",
        "In this attack, the ticket office and the goods store of the railway station were damaged and the Panadura police intervened and brought the situation under control.",
        "This is the second attack in the last 12 days of this month due to absence of trains.",
        "An official of the Panadura railway station said that immediately after the incident near the Prime Minister's office in Colombo, a large crowd came to the railway station to come to Colombo, and when they learned that the train had been cancelled, they behaved violently."
      ],
